t;<br />\n無論由咩Data 到港大微生物學系傳染病學講座教授袁國勇表示，麻疹只是輕微疾病，數日後便會痊癒，麻疹患者僅有0.1至0.3%會引發嚴重併發症導致死亡，呼籲市民毋須恐慌。<br />\n到尋日佢講:強調九成八人口有麻疹保護抗體，市民無需太擔憂，最重要是注意個人衞生。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得係過份擔心,同埋唔似糖尿病/心臟病藥 冇左會死<br />\n唔同你講大疫症死亡率無數<br />\n我相信唔係同一樣野"},{"pid":"d09dfd1dffd16bbb2879cba5081b391085ff79e6","tid":1086950,"uid":18721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:46:58.000Z","msg":"有市就有價 <br />\n仲要係香港 咁樣做真係好平常"},{"pid":"e1a8483a36f0a7be95ce2dc20d40cf8f9f49e025","tid":1086950,"uid":193893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:49:33.000Z","msg":"屌，香港啲中醫，全部都係大陸訓練出黎，點會識醫德係"},{"pid":"9db29d187453bf519b88c8fa0ffb5273396b85bd","tid":1086950,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:50:18.000Z","msg":"加價可能係唔想咁多人去搵佢 <br />\n唔係真係加你價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />覺得貴咪搵B醫生囉"},{"pid":"9f17e13f60b3ef6aafed9e69592e1cd97bb4eb8f","tid":1086950,"uid":34300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T06:08:21.000Z","msg":"中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1646505edf1eac72f9596f008f06fb70056ddadd","tid":1086950,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T06:11:26.000Z","msg":"中醫醫唔醫到麻疹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daacaf106e89d8621d93ec039a3becc78bf6f577","tid":1086950,"uid":41849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T06:11:31.000Z","msg":"講到中醫有得幫人打疫苗咁<br />\n咪又係冇權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470b6ab8d13b48af93a5d43b37171e2438ab3872","tid":1086950,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21b65aa9b8dc8a46805aadf51bcd72e9dabdbb0d","tid":1086950,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:38:41.000Z